Welcome to pyocs 👋

> Python ocs 自动化程序 ### 🏠 [Homepage](https://gitlab.gz.cvte.cn/python-tool/pyocs) ## Install 请阅读 [安装说明](https://kb.cvte.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=133389700) ```sh pip3 install pyocs --user ``` ## Usage 请阅读 [命令行工具使用说明](https://kb.cvte.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=135446441) ```sh pyocs --help ``` ## Prerequisites 仅用于开发环境下解决依赖问题 ```sh pip install -r requirements.txt ``` ## Documentation 请阅读 [KB文档专区](https://kb.cvte.com/display/TeamTVSW/Pyocs) ## Author 👤 **TSC-Python-Team** ## 🤝 Contributing Contributions, issues and feature requests are welcome!
Feel free to check [issues page](https://gitlab.gz.cvte.cn/python-tool/pyocs/issues). ## Show your support Give a ⭐ if this project helped you!
